        "jsCode": "// Calcula a data de referência (D-1) e janelas de comparação\nconst now = new Date();\nconst dRef = new Date(now);\ndRef.setDate(dRef.getDate() - 1);\nconst yyyy = dRef.getFullYear();\nconst mm = String(dRef.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0');\nconst dd = String(dRef.getDate()).padStart(2, '0');\nconst dataRef = `${yyyy}-${mm}-${dd}`;\n\n// Janelas para Meta/Google Ads (D-1)\nconst dayStart = `${dataRef}T00:00:00-03:00`;\nconst dayEnd = `${dataRef}T23:59:59-03:00`;\n\n// Para AdMob (formato YYYY-MM-DD)\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    data_referencia: dataRef,\n    day_start_iso: dayStart,\n    day_end_iso: dayEnd,\n    admob_date: { year: yyyy, month: dRef.getMonth() + 1, day: dRef.getDate() }\n  }\n}];"
